{"tid":2017147,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普正檢視美上市中企 是否符美會計準則","createTime":"2020-05-15T02:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T12:55:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"11c16bf93ffa691c1e291e4cbd6268a5204e3a61","tid":2017147,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，正檢視在美國上市的中國企業的賬目是否符合美國會計準則。<br />\n<br />\n他接受霍士新聞訪問時又指，採取強硬態度可能讓這些中國企業轉至倫敦或香港掛牌。<br />\n<br />\n此前，特朗普提及可能迫使中國企業除牌或禁止退休基金投資中企。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2466412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2466412&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=1d3c695b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2466412</a><br />\n<br />\nIn an interview on Fox Business Network&rsquo;s &ldquo;Mornings with Maria,&rdquo; Mr. Trump said in response to a question on the subject that he was looking &ldquo;very strongly&rdquo; at imposing such a rule on Chinese companies, which aren&rsquo;t currently required to follow the same accounting rules as U.S. companies listed on the New York Stock Exchange or Nasdaq.<br />\n<br />\nBut the president added: &ldquo;Let&rsquo;s say we do that. So what are they going to do? They&rsquo;re going to move their listing to London or someplace else. You see?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nA NYSE spokeswoman declined to comment.<br />\n<br />\nThe fight over regulation of Chinese companies dates back more than a decade, to when many Chinese companies went public on U.S. stock exchanges by merging with an American shell company. Such &ldquo;reverse mergers&rdquo; gave the Chinese companies access to a U.S. investor base with little upfront scrutiny from the Securities and Exchange Commission....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/trump-may-push-for-chinese-companies-to-follow-u-s-accounting-rules-for-stock-listings-11589459803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Ftrump-may-push-for-chinese-companies-to-follow-u-s-accounting-rules-for-stock-listings-11589459803&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=34ac2048\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/trump-may-push-for-chinese-companies-to-follow-u-s-accounting-rules-for-stock-listings-11589459803</a>"},{"pid":"1172e65b8f6079d4b2b82c48f009af59605eaff9","tid":2017147,"uid":299694,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:49:44.000Z","msg":"去訓啦trump,講多過做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d730dff6b2ca3164de9db653c75f37ff4f950db2","tid":2017147,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:38:50.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講，美國退休金無得買大中華股票"},{"pid":"115c4046fbcba739d4a9c033831d25801c929057","tid":2017147,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"做假呢啲野，支那最勁，點會咁易比美帝搵到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31bacccc6f5c99998b6dddca56d695e280afe2c","tid":2017147,"uid":198175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"唔覺唔覺, 金融戰開打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec2344071cb331450ec64f74be77e3f2287e0b5","tid":2017147,"uid":228794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"岩啦， 益香港， 抽新股仲正"},{"pid":"e3bfa8cd3997f0f7189ca0fe54851ae762323976","tid":2017147,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"115c4046fbcba739d4a9c033831d25801c929057","tid":2017147,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"做假呢啲野，支那最勁，點會咁易比美帝搵到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"Muddy Water幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"